modName: The Ashen Race - Chargen Morph patch
summary:
This is an Ashen Race compatability patch for the Chargen morphs and Chargen ECE morphs.

It will enable the morph same sliders for the Ashen Race as the vanilla races.
descriptionHtml:
My first mod!

This is an Ashen Race compatability patch for the Chargen morphs and Chargen ECE morphs.

It will enable the morph same sliders for the Ashen Race as the vanilla races.

Requirements:
The Ashen Race can be found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/8583/?
Chargen extension here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36925/?

Compatablility:
I made this using The Ashen Race version 6.5 and Chargen Extension version 2.1.4



Credits go out to Seren4XX for making the Ashen Race, one of my favorite and most used races.
Credits go out to expired6978 for making the Chargen Extension mod.
Credits go out to Nuska for making custom TRI files that work using Chargen Extension mod.
author: Zerpentor
